<p class="">The fact of the matter is that in Glasgow there was a very large opinion against the National Government in spite of the demoralisation that took place in the Labour party owing to the treachery of the leader of the Labour party and the extraordinary circumstances that resulted during that period of crisis.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
