            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-373951b5-8180-45ef-9b97-46b6821a9c52" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1939-04-27/debates/f18e969a-d592-4ad8-8385-418a7768c226/CompulsoryMilitaryTraining#contribution-373951b5-8180-45ef-9b97-46b6821a9c52">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
