        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-847d3e92-ac04-47dc-8fd6-a2b0f938328f'>
            
<p class="">Adjourned accordingly at Twenty-Five Minutes after Eleven o'Clock.</p>
        </div>
